      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's what i mean though. \"vital part of the world\" sounds so heavy and fake. it's just words. in reality, my boss only pings me when i'm late on a task, and my \"friends\" are just people i haven't spoken to in months. if i just vanished, the only thing that would change is a little less noise in the slack channels. it would be so quiet. wouldn't it be easier for everyone if things were just... quiet?",
